# 🧊 LiveCold — Complete Presentation Guide for Judges

> **Cold Chain Intelligence Platform** — Real-time IoT monitoring, AI-driven diversion decisions, and live SOP compliance for India's ₹2.5 Lakh Crore cold chain industry.

---

## 🎯 The Problem We're Solving

India loses **₹92,000 Crore** worth of food annually due to cold chain failures. A single truck with a faulty reefer unit carrying ₹25 Lakh of vaccines can lose its entire cargo in 30 minutes — and nobody knows until it's too late.

**LiveCold** is an end-to-end intelligent platform that:
- Monitors every shipment in real-time via IoT sensors
- Detects anomalies BEFORE they become disasters
- Makes AI-powered diversion decisions in milliseconds
- Routes trucks to the nearest compatible cold storage hub
- Keeps drivers informed via WhatsApp-style notifications
- Ensures full SOP compliance with a live RAG pipeline

---

